headline: Allergan Aesthetics Emphasizes Commitment to Innovation, Science and a Patient Centric Approach at AMWC 2025
summary: Allergan Aesthetics, an AbbVie company, the industry leader in aesthetics globally, demonstrates how to elevate the patient experience and achieve optimal treatment outcomes with new AA Signature program at the Anti-Aging and Aesthetics Medicine World Congress (AMWC) in Monaco from Thursday, March 27– Saturday, March 29, 2025.
